(119, 1, '2015-09-16 16:20:37', '2015-09-16 16:20:37', 'Learn more about Bridgeland by visiting its state-of-the-art Welcome Center overlooking majestic Lake Bridgeland.\r\n\r\nUpon arrival, visitors will be greeted by a warm, attentive and knowledgeable staff member who can walk through an interactive and engaging presentation on the community. A 60-inch touch-screen plasma map allows visitors to view their future homes with renderings that showcase everything from a regional perspective of the development to a microcosm of each individual homesite, as well as elevations, prices and builders. The presentation vividly illustrates Bridgeland’s future plans with conceptual maps, visual representations of planned amenities and an aerial photo of the entire 11,400-acre community.\r\n\r\nAside from the presentation, other touch screens allow visitors to conduct a search of available homes based on builder, price, square footage and/or specific features.\r\n\r\nBridgeland Welcome Center\r\n16919 North Bridgeland Lake Pkwy.\r\nCypress, TX 77433\r\n\r\nVisiting hours are 10 a.m. to 5 p.m. Monday through Saturday and noon to 5 p.m. Sunday. Call us at (281) 304-5588 or toll free at (866) 232-0270. You can also email us at <a href="mailto:welcomecenter@bridgeland.com">welcomecenter@bridgeland.com</a>.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-238" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/WC.jpg" alt="WC" width="1024" height="683" />', 'Welcome Center', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'welcome-center', '', '', '2015-09-21 15:43:19', '2015-09-21 15:43:19', '', 117, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=119', 0, 'page', '', 0),
