(144, 1, '2015-09-16 16:43:32', '2015-09-16 16:43:32', '[contact-form-7 id="338" title="Contact Us"]\r\n\r\n<iframe class="contact-page" style="border: 0;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d13828.142527003609!2d-95.73529244999996!3d29.949653700000006!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x86412a06400268f9%3A0x2cdbdea23e7194c!2sBridgeland%2C+Cypress%2C+TX+77433!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1442344675414" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<em><strong>Bridgeland Welcome Center</strong></em>\r\n\r\n16919 N. Bridgeland Lake Pkwy.\r\nCypress, TX 77433\r\n(281) 304-5588 or (866) 232-0270\r\n<a href="mailto:welcomecenter@bridgeland.com">welcomecenter@bridgeland.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>From US 290 (the Northwest Freeway)</em></strong>\r\n\r\nTraveling northwest on US 290 outbound from Houston, take the Spring-Cypress/Cypress-Rosehill/Fry Road exit. Turn left on Fry Road (2nd traffic light). Proceed south on Fry Road for approximately 2. 5 miles. Turn right on North Bridgleand Lake Parkway, the main entrance to Bridgeland.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>From SH 99 (the Grand Parkway)</em></strong>\r\n\r\nComing south from the Grand Parkway, exit Bridgeland Creek Parkway and turn right at the light. If coming north from I-10, exit the Grand Parkway at Bridgeland Creek Parkway and turn left. Remain straight on House Hahl/ Hidden Pass until taking a left on East Creekside Bend. Follow along until turning left at Josey Ranch Road. The entrance to the Welcome Center will be ahead on the right.', 'Contact Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-us', '', '', '2015-09-25 15:59:43', '2015-09-25 15:59:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=144', 4, 'page', '', 0),
