(165, 1, '2015-09-16 19:40:32', '2015-09-16 19:40:32', 'Bridgeland has announced plans for the first of several village centers that will include dining, retail, medical offices and employment opportunities. Lakeland Village Center will be adjacent to the community of <a href="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/living-in-bridgeland/communities/current-communities/lakeland-heights/">Lakeland Heights</a>, allowing this unique shopping center to be within walking distance for residents.\r\n\r\nPre-leasing is underway and <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/blog/bridgeland-breaks-ground-lakeland-village-center" target="_blank">CVS/pharmacy®</a> has been announced as the anchor tenant. Updates and additional tenants will be posted as soon as they are available.\r\n\r\n%CODE3%', 'Lakeland Village Center', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lakeland-village-center', '', '', '2015-09-21 16:03:38', '2015-09-21 16:03:38', '', 140, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=165', 1, 'page', '', 0),
