(175, 1, '2015-09-16 19:41:46', '2015-09-16 19:41:46', '<p style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>Bridging Farms and Families</strong></em>\r\n<strong>Second Sunday of Every Month</strong>\r\n<strong>12:30-3:30</strong></p>\r\nRun by a team of Bridgeland volunteers who are dedicated to bringing fresh, homegrown food to Cypress residents, the market’s mission is to support and promote local food providers, while also offering educational events that enlighten consumers on the value of shopping locally.\r\n\r\nRain or shine, the market is held on the second Sunday of every month at Lakeland Activity Center, 16902 Bridgeland Landing.\r\n\r\nFor more information, visit <a href="http://www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org/">www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org</a>.\r\n<div class="media media-element-container media-default"><img class="alignnone wp-image-521 size-full" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/bl_fm120.jpg" alt="bl_fm120" width="1024" height="683" /></div>', 'Farmers Market', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'farmers-market', '', '', '2015-09-24 21:08:12', '2015-09-24 21:08:12', '', 142, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=175', 1, 'page', '', 0),
