(295, 1, '2015-09-21 15:48:51', '2015-09-21 15:48:51', 'Within the 3,000 acres of open space found in Bridgeland, there are more than 400 acres of parks, 900 acres of lakes and a wide array of playgrounds, tennis courts, picnic pavilions and trails to enjoy.\r\n\r\nDuring the heat of summer, residents can stay cool at Lakeland Activity Center, a 6,000-sqaure-foot amenity that features two 30-foot tower slides. The site also serves as a hub for community events hosted by Bridgeland’s on-site Activities Director, including daily exercise classes, weekly neighborhood meetings and gatherings, as well as camps and workshops for the youth of the community.\r\n\r\nEventually, shops, restaurants and entertainment venues will also be found in Bridgeland''s village centers and the community-wide Town Center.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-294" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/CF014068.jpg" alt="CF014068" width="1024" height="747" />', 'Playing in Bridgeland', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '138-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-21 15:48:51', '2015-09-21 15:48:51', '', 138, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/138-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
