(348, 1, '2015-09-22 17:51:36', '2015-09-22 17:51:36', '<h3>Disc Golf Tournament</h3>\r\nThe Oak Meadow Open on September 26th is a PDGA sanctioned disc golf tournament. Players from Bridgeland and all over Texas will compete in professional and amateur divisions for both men and women. All players will receive a custom Bridgeland putter from Gateway discs. There will be an in round closest to the pin contest and ring of fire event after the tournament for a chance to win more prizes. Check in begins at 7:30 and we will have a player meeting at 8:30. The event is 2 rounds of 18 holes. Register online at <a href="http://dgscene.com/oakmeadowopen" target="_blank">dgscene.com/oakmeadowopen</a>.', 'Oak Meadow Park Open', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'oak-meadow-park-open', '', '', '2015-09-22 19:38:05', '2015-09-22 19:38:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?post_type=ecwd_event&#038;p=348', 0, 'ecwd_event', '', 0);
