><strong><u> Register</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong>Building Brains - Elementary</strong>\r\n\r\nIn this camp, students build simple machines using gears, levers and pulleys and then motorize them using Lego and K''Nex educational kits and curriculum – all while building math and science skills. Using the newest Lego educational kit, students challenge each other to create, build and test the best design. Students will learn why a machine works and how to manipulate a machine to go faster or slower. Fine motor skills, critical thinking skills, imagination and confidence will increase in this fun-filled atmosphere.\r\n<table border="0" width="786" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Session</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Registration</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Fees</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Info</strong></td>\r\n<td colspan="2"><strong>Register</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>June 8 - June 12 (Full Day)</td>\r\n<td>Closes Jun 5th</td>\r\n<td>$285.00/$295.00</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/"><strong><u> Info</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/#register"><strong><u> Register</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>June 29 - July 2 (Full Day)</td>\r\n<td>Closes Jun 26th</td>\r\n<td>$230.00/$240.00</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/"><strong><u> Info</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/#register"><strong><u> Register</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>July 20- July 24 (Full Day)</td>\r\n<td>Closes Jul 17th</td>\r\n<td>$285.00/$295.00</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/"><strong><u> Info</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Ass