(416, 1, '2015-03-17 16:56:30', '2015-03-17 16:56:30', 'Back for its eighth year, Bridgeland’s <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/events/nature-fest">Nature Fest</a> is set to roar into town on Saturday, May 2<sup>nd</sup>  with a wild combination of exotic creatures, lively activities and tantalizing food trucks. Event attendees will also have the opportunity to see and interact with a rare and respected figure in the wildlife kingdom – <a href="http://www.jackhanna.com/" target="_blank">Jack Hanna</a>, a long-time animal advocate that has been featured on shows like Good Morning America, The Late Show with David Letterman and other well-known, nationally-syndicated programs.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<div class="media media-element-container media-default"><img class="media-element file-default alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/Jack%20and%20Tiger.JPG" alt="" width="308" height="462" /></div>\r\n“I’m looking forward to being a part of Nature Fest,” said Hanna. “Along with being a great adventure for the whole family, the event inspires people to learn and care about wildlife and the natural world – things I’m passionate about.”\r\n\r\nWild things of all ages are sure to enjoy an on-site petting zoo with unique animals like zebras, kangaroos and wallabies; armadillo races, world-class roaming entertainers, educational reptile and bird shows, as well as many other family-friendly activities. While admission and some activities are free of charge, others require a small fee, with a portion of proceeds benefiting Habitat for Humanity Northwest County, a non-profit organization that builds affordable housing for families in need throughout Harris County.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, a pack of gourmet food trucks, including Houston favorites like Bernie’s Burger Bus, Custom Confections, Golden Grill, The Waffle Bus and Menchie’s, will be set-up to satisfy unruly cravings.\r\n\r\n“Beyond providing a fun-filled day for families, Nature Fest continues to bring attention to Bridgeland’s commitment to the area’s environment and ecosystem,” said Peter Houghton, Bridgeland’s Vice President of Master Planned Communities.\r\n\r\nNature Fest will run from 10 a.m. to 5 p.m. at Oak Meadow Park in Bridgeland, 17730 House Hahl Road. Hanna’s three performances are scheduled for 12 p.m., 1:30 p.m. and 3 p.m.\r\n\r\nSponsors of this year’s event include <a href="http://www.charlesdyeriv.com/" target="_blank">Charles E. Dyer IV, DDS, MS, PC</a>, a returning Title Sponsor, <a href="http://www.beazer.com/" target="_blank">Beazer Homes</a>, <a href="http://www.browngay.com/" target="_blank">Brown &amp; Gay Engineers, Inc.,</a> <a href="http://www.costelloinc.com/" target="_blank">Costello</a>, <a href="http://www.deltawestenv.com/" target="_blank">Delta West Environmental</a>, <a href="http://www.gulfcoastcorp.com/">Gulf Coast Landscaping Services, Inc</a>., <a href="http://www.perryhomes.com/" target="_blank">Perry Homes</a>, <a href="http://www.pcmi-us.com/" target="_blank">Planned Community Management</a>, <a href="http://www.rkci.com/" target="_blank">Raba Kistner</a>, <a href="http://www.sphllp.com/" target="_blank">Schwartz, Page &amp; Harding, L.L.P.</a>, <a href="http://www.terrainsolutionsinc.com/" target="_blank">Terrain Solutions, Inc</a>., <a href="http://www.texaspremierdental.com/" target="_blank">Texas Premier Dental</a>, <a href="http://www.realestatewithamy.com/" target="_blank">The Lippincott Team</a>, <a href="http://www.thelittlegym.com/houstoncopperfieldtx" target="_blank">The Little Gym of Copperfield</a>, <a href="http://www.westin-homes.com/" target="_blank">Westin Homes</a>, Allgreen Associates, Grindel Consulting and  Municipal Accounts and Consulting.\r\n\r\nKeep up-to-date on Nature Fest news and other Bridgeland activities on Facebook,<a href="http://www.facebook.com/Bridgelandcommunity">facebook.com/Bridgelandcommunity</a>, Twitter, <a href="http://www.twitter.com/bridgelandtweet">twitter.com/BridgelandTweet </a>and Instagram,<a href="http://www.instagram.com/Bridgelandbalance">instagram.com/Bridgelandbalance</a>.', 'Nature Fest to Feature Performances From Jack Hanna May 2', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nature-fest-to-feature-performances-from-jack-hanna-may-2', '', '', '2015-09-24 16:57:02', '2015-09-24 16:57:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?p=416', 0, 'post', '', 0),
