(456, 1, '2015-10-14 19:00:28', '2015-10-14 19:00:28', 'How would you like to win your furry friend a one-hour mini session with <a href="http://www.barkoutloudphotography.com/index.php">Bark Out Loud Photography</a>? In honor of Howl-O-Ween Fest, Bridgeland’s marketing department is hosting a virtual pet costume contest with just that as the prize! If you think your dog has the most ''spooktacular'' Halloween attire, send a message with a snapshot of him or her to Bridgeland’s <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/blog/www.facebook.com/bridgelandcommunity">Facebook</a>. They’ll post it in an album and ask followers to ''like'' their favorite picture. The photo with the most ''likes'' by Friday, Oct. 24th gets the prize!', 'Howl-O-Ween Fest Virtual Costume Contest', '', 'future', 'open', 'open', '', 'howl-o-ween-fest-virtual-costume-contest', '', '', '2015-09-24 19:01:14', '2015-09-24 19:01:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?p=456', 0, 'post', '', 0),
