(470, 1, '2014-08-25 19:07:42', '2014-08-25 19:07:42', 'With summer winding down, The Farmers Market at <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/">Bridgeland</a> on Sept. 14 will offer shoppers the last of seasonal, summertime produce from 12:30-3:30 p.m., as well as the opportunity to learn from experienced gardener Stephanie Baker, who will lead a class focused on the fundamentals of successful fall vegetable gardening.<span class="caption none media-image alignright size-medium wp-image-2384"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/septembermarket-278x3004jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/September_Market-278x300_4.jpg?itok=6LmCEcBi" alt="September Market To Offer" width="204" height="220" /></a></span>\r\n\r\nBaker teaches a garden-based science curriculum to Cy-Fair, Spring Branch and Montgomery ISD schools through having students plant seeds, harvest vegetables and observe caterpillars and butterflies, and is also the owner of Ready to Grow Gardens. Starting at 1 p.m. on Sunday, Baker’s class will cover how to prepare a raised vegetable bed, the best planting schedules and tips on caring for and fertilizing fall crops.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nA new vendor, Popcart Icepops, will sell its handmade, all-natural popsicles that come in fruit or dairy-based varieties like Blackberry Lime Verbena and Chi Latte.\r\n\r\nMerchants will also bring along the last of their summer harvest, including watermelons, summer squash, sweet corn, eggplant, zucchini, local honey, cucumbers, peas and a variety of peppers.\r\n\r\nHeld on the second Sunday of each month, The Farmers Market at Bridgeland is located near the Lakeland Activity Center, 16902 Bridgeland Landing. To see a full list of participating vendors, visit <a href="http://www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org/">www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org.</a>\r\n\r\nLearn more about Bridgeland, a wholly owned subsidiary of <a href="http://www.howardhughes.com/">The Howard Hughes Corporation</a> and part of <a href="http://www.thewoodlands.com/">The Woodlands Development Company</a>, at <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/">www.bridgeland.com</a>.', 'Bridgeland''s September Market to Offer Last of Summer Produce and Fall Gardening Class', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bridgelands-september-market-to-offer-last-of-summer-produce-and-fall-gardening-class', '', '', '2015-09-24 19:08:22', '2015-09-24 19:08:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?p=470', 0, 'post', '', 0),
