(488, 1, '2014-05-13 19:39:47', '2014-05-13 19:39:47', 'Bridgeland’s 7<sup>th</sup> Annual Nature Fest was a wild success with $7,800 raised for Habitat for Humanity NWHC and Staples Safari Zoo, the two nonprofits the event supports each year.<span class="caption none media-image alignright size-medium wp-image-2323"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/bridgelandnaturefestjpg-300x2254jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BridgelandNatureFest.jpg-300x225_4.jpg?itok=OUpzCSjh" alt="BridgelandNatureFest.jpg" width="220" height="165" /></a></span>\r\n\r\nEntrance into Nature Fest was free; however, a few activities required a small donation that benefited one of the two organizations. Approximately $3,000 was raised for the local chapter of Habitat for Humanity and another $4,800 was gathered for Staples Safari Zoo.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nHabitat NWHC will use its proceeds to build safe and affordable housing for families in need. Since the affiliate’s inception in 1989, volunteers and receiving families have built more than 200 homes, which are typically about 1,200 square feet.\r\n\r\nBridgeland and Habitat NWHC have a long history of partnership and the development has donated nearly $21,600 to the non-profit since 2009.\r\n\r\n“Our partnership with Bridgeland continues to grow each year” said Chad Greer, Habitat NWHC’s corporate relations manager.  We’re very fortunate to work with an organization that understands the importance of providing the resources needed to make our community a better place to live, work, play and raise a family.”\r\n\r\nMoney raised for Staples Safari Zoo will go towards the care and rehabilitation of the organization’s 120 rescued animals.\r\n\r\nBridgeland, a strong community partner and supporter, is a wholly-owned subsidiary of <a href="http://www.howardhughes.com/">The Howard Hughes Corporation</a> and part of <a href="http://www.thewoodlands.com/">The Woodlands Development Company</a>.', 'Bridgeland''s Nature Fest Attendees Raise $7,800 for Nonprofits', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bridgelands-nature-fest-attendees-raise-7800-for-nonprofits', '', '', '2015-09-24 19:40:26', '2015-09-24 19:40:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?p=488', 0, 'post', '', 0),
