(500, 1, '2014-03-12 20:06:53', '2014-03-12 20:06:53', 'The countdown to Spring Break is finally in the single digits! Whether you''re jetting off for an exotic getaway or enjoying a relaxing staycation in town, Bridgeland Bill wants to join.\r\n\r\nConsequently, we''d like for you do one of two things to win our latest social media contest:<span class="caption none media-image alignright size-medium wp-image-2280"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/teaser-picture-256x3004jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Teaser-Picture--256x300_4.jpg?itok=Oi-GKorP" alt="Teaser Picture" width="188" height="220" /></a></span>\r\n\r\nTeaser Picture\r\n\r\n1) Stage a ''Spring Break-themed'' picture with a Bridgeland Bill stuffed animal, something we''re giving away for free at the Welcome Center. The whole family can be in the photo or it can just be Bill - we''re keeping it open to encourage creativity. We ask that everything be family friendly, though.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<strong><em>or</em></strong>\r\n\r\n2) For those of you who don''t have a Bridgeland Bill stuffed animal or can''t pick one up, simply tag #BackpackingBill in your Spring Break pictures'' captions.\r\n\r\nBill will choose a picture he feels embodies what Spring Break is all about - fun! Photos can be posted on our Facebook wall, tweeted at @BridgelandTweet, tagged on Instagram (#BackpackingBill) and/or emailed to<a href="mailto:welcomecenter@bridgeland.com">welcomecenter@bridgeland.com</a> - whatever is easiest for you!\r\n\r\nWhat''s the prize, you ask? The lucky winner will receive a $100 Visa gift card and a visit from Bridgeland Bill at a birthday party or event. Free money and a fun visitor? That''s a winning combination!\r\n\r\nGet snappin''! We can''t wait to see all the places Bill travels to.', 'Bridgeland''s Latest Social Media Contest Calls for Spring Break Snapshots', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '