(524, 1, '2015-09-24 21:11:37', '2015-09-24 21:11:37', 'Bridgeland''s expansive waterways and shaded trail system make it an ideal location for competitive sporting events. In fact, the community has hosted the Cypress Triathlon for the last seven years, helping it grow into the largest stand-alone sprint tri in the region.\n\nAlthough it varies from year-to-year, Bridgeland tends to also serve as the location for a number of local Thanksgiving and Christmas-themed races.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-523" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/120805-BRIDGELAND-TRI-1223.jpg" alt="120805 BRIDGELAND TRI 1223" width="1024" height="683" />\n\n[su_tabs vertical="yes"]\n\n[su_tab title="tab1"]\n\nJuly 26, 2015\n\n550-meter swim,12.5-mile bike, 3.1-mile run\n\n<a href="http://cypresstriathlon.com/" target="_blank">Registration</a>\n\n[/su_tab]\n\n[su_tab title="tab2"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/su_tab]\n\n[su_tab title="tab3"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/su_tab]\n\n[/su_tabs]', 'Races & Triathlons', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '181-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-24 21:11:37', '2015-09-24 21:11:37', '', 181, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/181-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
